                     <interp inst="t18241028-14-person218" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman, and assisted Baker.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18241028-14-person219">
                  THOMAS 
                  MANNING
               <interp inst="t18241028-14-person219" type="surname" value="MANNING"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18241028-14-person219" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18241028-14-person219" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I found the crow-bar in the cellar.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had been to my aunt's, and on passing this area a man rushed out, and caught hold of me: I fell in, and was getting up when the watchman drove me down.</p>
